c: 35
v: 42
t: "(Abakaafiiri be Makkah) baalayira Katonda mu kukakasa ebirayiro byabwe (ne bagamba nti) singa omutiisa alibajjira bagenda kubeerera ddala abasinga obulungamu okusinga (abantu bonna abaali babaddewo), awo nno omutiisa (Muhammad) bwe yabajjira tekyabongera okugyako okwesamba (omubaka)"